-- NATO Invites Pakistan’s Zardari to Chicago to Discuss Security
-- B y   F a r h a n   S h a r i f
-- 2012-05-15T13:47:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-15/nato-invites-pakistan-s-zardari-to-chicago-to-discuss-security.html
Pakistan President Asif Ali Zardari
was invited to the Chicago summit by North Atlantic Treaty
Organization Secretary General Anders Fogh Rasmussen to discuss
security issues and Afghanistan’s future, the president’s
spokesman said in a statement.  Zardari will consider the invitation on the government’s
advice, spokesman  Farhatullah Babar  said in the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Farhan Sharif in Karachi at 
 fsharif2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
